beer.beer_description:
Off the back of 2 DIPA's we loved, the only reasonable progression was to a TIPA (and if we keep following this trajectory we'll be at QIPA by the end of the year). Or are these all just fancy names for Imperial IPA's? Who knows.

Being our biggest hazy IPA to date we decided to give it a very healthy does of Ekuanot Cryo in the whirlpool (ok, in reality Mike had a moment and hopped it as if we're standard T90 hops....and a full size batch ?).

This TIPA was then double dry hopped with a blend of some of our favourite batches of Citra, Simcoe and Idaho-7. Think dank tropical fruits, Honeydew Melon and Papaya.

items.badge_description: With the Beijing 2022 Winter Olympics debuting this month, here's a winter competition for you. Don’t worry, you won’t need to land a Triple Salchow or a Double McTwist 1260 to unlock this badge. Just drink a beer!

There's beer in them thar hills! You're setting off on your journey through the world of beer, but be sure to take a little time to get to know each brewery as you go. That's a beer from 185 different breweries. Try 5 more for Level 38!

items.badge_description: January 24 marks the very first day that beer was offered in a canned container - way back in 1935. Celebrate Beer Can Appreciation Day by cracking a cold one and toasting to this popular beverage vessel and all of its creative reiterations.

Canning is all the rage and it's not hard to see why - travels well, more environmentally friendly, and no need to carry your bottle opener. That's 85 checkins with the serving style of Can. Try 5 more for Level 18! Want to learn more about this badge? Check out our podcast
We believe in IPA and you should too. You certainly have a taste for the hops! That's 65 different IPAs. Try 5 more for Level 14! Want to learn more about this badge? Check out our podcast

You may not be able to see through the haze, but that juicy, hoppy goodness goes down smooth. What started as a trend is here to stay. That's 40 different beers with the style of IPA - New England / Hazy, Pale Ale - New England / Hazy, IPA - Milkshake, or Pale Ale - Milkshake. Try 5 more for Level 9!
Do you come from the land down under, where beer does flow, and men chunder? That's at least 45 different beers from Australia. Try 5 more for Level 10.
